Package bto.Interfaces

package bto.Interfaces
  • Interfaces
    Class
    Description
    IApplicationController
    Interface defining the contract for managing BTO housing project applications.
    IAuthController
    Interface defining the contract for user authentication and account management.
    IBookingController
    Interface defining the contract for managing flat bookings for BTO housing projects.
    IEnquiryController
    Interface defining the contract for managing enquiries in the BTO housing system.
    IProjectController
    Interface defining the contract for managing BTO housing projects.
    IReceiptGenerator
    Interface defining the contract for generating receipts for BTO flat bookings.
    IRegistrationController
    Interface defining the contract for managing officer registrations for BTO housing projects.
    IReportController
    Interface defining the contract for generating and formatting reports for the BTO housing system.
    IWithdrawalController
    Interface defining the contract for managing withdrawal requests from applicants.
